      "updated_at": "2016-03-09 20:00:45 UTC",
      "body": "I have a fix that allows space after annotations if the annotation is only a single identifier `@identifier` (no `@annotation(foo)`) AND the right hand side fits in a single line up to either the first `=` or the last token of the statement (for example `@root class Token`). This at least allows single line definitions of common annotations like `@inline`, `@tailrec`, etc."
    },
